{{draft}}{{infobox religious building | religious_affiliation = | image = Ise Sarutahiko Shrine.jpg | deity = [[Sarutahiko Ōkami]] }} '''[[Sarutahiko Shrine]]''' is a [[shinto shrine]] in [[Ise, Mie]].<ref>https://www.sarutahikojinja.or.jp/english/</ref> It is a [[beppyo shrine]] and a [[Hokora]] in the [[Modern system of ranked Shinto shrines|modern system of ranked shinto shrines]].
The priests of the shrine are direct descendants of [[Sarutahiko Ōkami]].<ref>{{Cite web |title=Dedicated to Sarutahiko Okami, the Kami of Guidance｜みちひらきの大神 猿田彦神社 |url=https://www.sarutahikojinja.or.jp/english/ |access-date=2023-10-21 |website=www.sarutahikojinja.or.jp}}</ref> == Images == <gallery widths="200px" heights="150px"> Image:猿田彦神社 - 大鳥居.jpg|Torii Image:猿田彦神社 - 手水舎.jpg|Chozuya Sarume Shrine.jpg|Sarume Shrine Image:猿田彦神社 - たから石.jpg|[[Iwakura rock]] Image:猿田彦神社 - 子宝池.jpg|Pond File:Hakutaka Barrels at Sarutahiko Shrine, Ise.jpg|Sake barrels </gallery>
